-- Romania Reduces Pollution Tax on Cars by 25%, Mediafax Reports
-- B y   A n d r a   T i m u
-- 2011-12-16T07:45:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-16/romania-reduces-pollution-tax-on-cars-by-25-mediafax-reports.html
Romania ’s parliament lowered a
pollution tax on cars by 25 percent,  Mediafax  reported, citing
an Environment Ministry document.  The level of the tax depends on a car engine’s capacity,
pollution level and age, according to the Bucharest-based news
service.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andra Timu in Bucharest at 
 atimu@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  